### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### MelaniApp API — REST Client (VSCode REST Client extension)
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Flujo rápido:
###   1. Login → copia el accessToken → pega en @token
###   2. Usa los endpoints protegidos con Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = PEGAR_ACCESS_TOKEN_AQUI
@refreshToken = PEGAR_REFRESH_TOKEN_AQUI
@clienteId = PEGAR_CLIENTE_ID_AQUI
@alumnoId = PEGAR_ALUMNO_ID_AQUI
@routineId = PEGAR_ROUTINE_ID_AQUI
@weightLogId = PEGAR_WEIGHT_LOG_ID_AQUI
@today = 2025-05-14

### ─── AUTH ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Login Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@melaniapp.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

###

### Login Cliente (Melani)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "melani@trainer.com",
  "password": "Melani123!"
}

###

### Refresh access token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

###

### Logout (revoca el refresh token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

###

### /me — usuario actual
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── USERS — Admin ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Listar todos los clientes
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/clientes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Crear cliente
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/clientes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "GymCenter",
  "email": "gymcenter@mail.com",
  "password": "Gym123456!",
  "clientType": "GYM"
}

###

### Detalle de un cliente
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/clientes/{{clienteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Activar / desactivar cliente
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/clientes/{{clienteId}}/toggle-active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Alumnos de un cliente (vista admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/clientes/{{clienteId}}/alumnos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── USERS — Cliente ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Mis alumnos
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/alumnos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Crear alumno
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/alumnos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Ana",
  "apellido": "García",
  "email": "ana@gmail.com",
  "password": "Ana12345!",
  "telefono": "+54 9 11 1234-0000"
}

###

### Detalle de alumno
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/alumnos/{{alumnoId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── ROUTINES ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [ALUMNO] Mis rutinas
GET {{baseUrl}}/routines/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Todas las rutinas de mis alumnos
GET {{baseUrl}}/routines
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Rutinas de un alumno específico
GET {{baseUrl}}/routines/alumno/{{alumnoId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Crear rutina
POST {{baseUrl}}/routines
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "alumnoId": {{alumnoId}},
  "name": "Rutina Tren Superior",
  "days": [
    {
      "day": "Lunes",
      "exercises": [
        { "id": "ex1", "name": "Press de banca", "sets": 3, "reps": 12, "rest": 60, "notes": "" },
        { "id": "ex2", "name": "Dominadas", "sets": 3, "reps": 8, "rest": 90, "notes": "Asistidas si es necesario" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "day": "Jueves",
      "exercises": [
        { "id": "ex3", "name": "Press militar", "sets": 3, "reps": 10, "rest": 60, "notes": "" },
        { "id": "ex4", "name": "Elevaciones laterales", "sets": 3, "reps": 15, "rest": 45, "notes": "" }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

###

### Copiar rutina a otros alumnos
POST {{baseUrl}}/routines/{{routineId}}/copy
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetAlumnoIds": [{{alumnoId}}]
}

###

### Eliminar rutina
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/routines/{{routineId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── WEIGHT LOGS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [ALUMNO] Mi historial de peso
GET {{baseUrl}}/weight-logs/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Historial de peso de un alumno
GET {{baseUrl}}/weight-logs/{{alumnoId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Registrar peso
POST {{baseUrl}}/weight-logs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "alumnoId": {{alumnoId}},
  "date": "{{today}}",
  "weight": 62.5,
  "notes": "Mañana en ayunas"
}

###

### Eliminar registro de peso
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/weight-logs/{{weightLogId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── WORKOUT LOGS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [ALUMNO] Mis entrenos
GET {{baseUrl}}/workout-logs/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### [ALUMNO] Entreno de un día específico
GET {{baseUrl}}/workout-logs/me/{{today}}/{{routineId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### [ALUMNO] Marcar ejercicios como hechos
PUT {{baseUrl}}/workout-logs/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "{{today}}",
  "routineId": {{routineId}},
  "exercises": [
    {
      "exerciseId": "ex1",
      "completed": true,
      "sets": [
        { "done": true, "weight": 50, "reps": 12 },
        { "done": true, "weight": 52.5, "reps": 10 },
        { "done": false, "weight": 55, "reps": 8 }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

###

### Historial de entrenos de un alumno
GET {{baseUrl}}/workout-logs/{{alumnoId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Log de un día específico
GET {{baseUrl}}/workout-logs/{{alumnoId}}/{{today}}/{{routineId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Upsert log de entreno (crea o actualiza)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/workout-logs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "alumnoId": {{alumnoId}},
  "date": "{{today}}",
  "routineId": {{routineId}},
  "exercises": [
    {
      "exerciseId": "ex1",
      "completed": true,
      "sets": [
        { "done": true, "weight": 50, "reps": 12 },
        { "done": true, "weight": 52.5, "reps": 10 },
        { "done": false, "weight": 55, "reps": 8 }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
